## ğŸš¨ Severity Summary

### ğŸ”´ CRITICAL Issues (Must Fix Before Deployment)

| Gap ID | Issue | Impact | Location | Effort |
|--------|-------|--------|----------|--------|
| **GAP-001** | Missing authentication endpoints | Users cannot login, logout, or refresh tokens | Backend `/api/v1/auth/*` missing | 3-4 days |
| **GAP-002** | Provider type mismatch | 8 of 12 LLM providers inaccessible from UI | `frontend/src/lib/api/types.ts:43` | 1-2 days |
| **GAP-003** | Hardcoded WebSocket URL | All WebSocket connections fail on non-localhost deployments | `frontend/src/api/jailbreak.ts:19` | 0.5 days |

### ğŸŸ  High Priority Issues (Fix Within Sprint 1)

| Gap ID | Issue | Impact | Effort |
|--------|-------|--------|--------|
| **GAP-004** | Missing `refresh_expires_in` field | Token refresh logic incomplete | 0.5 days |
| **GAP-005** | No admin panel frontend | 14 admin endpoints inaccessible | 3-5 days |
| **GAP-006** | No metrics dashboard | 11 metrics endpoints inaccessible | 2-3 days |
| **GAP-007** | Deprecated API client still used | Maintenance burden, inconsistent patterns | 1-2 days |
| **GAP-008** | 7 missing error classes | Error handling incomplete | 1-2 days |
| **GAP-009** | Token type casing mismatch | `bearer` vs `Bearer` causes TypeScript issues | 0.5 days |
| **GAP-010** | Technique enum mismatch | 7+ techniques unavailable in UI | 1 day |
| **GAP-011** | Inconsistent WebSocket URLs | Some WS connections work, others fail | 0.5 days |

### ğŸŸ¡ Medium Priority Issues (Fix Within Sprint 2)

|--------|-------|--------|--------|
